{"tid":544431,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黃心穎擔正女一做丫鬟　唔覺得太遲：自己心態上ready","createTime":"2018-01-29T13:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T08:39:15.000Z","uid":143915,"like":8,"dislike":184,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ad4c0ffd764e5591c97cbf6bc4e33fcbfbbf51","tid":544431,"uid":143915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/212447_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F212447_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7af18f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃心穎首次做女一，與洪永城於古裝新劇《丫鬟大聯盟》合作。（陳順禎攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《學是學非》兩位是非精黃心穎同湯洛雯於無綫新劇《丫鬟大聯盟》再次合作，而該劇更係黃心穎入行以來首次擔正做女一，今午她出席造型活動時，就表示十分感恩。「話快又唔係，話遲又唔算，自己心態上ready，幸好今次呢部劇係喜劇，所以唔算好大壓力。但其實搞笑都難，同埋用多了力。」<br />\n<br />\n劇中黃心穎將會是丫鬟的阿姐，除與湯洛雯有不少女人爭吵戲之外，亦會與洪永城有感情戲，但她笑言最多也是攬攬錫錫。劇集將於下星期開拍，問到是否要在工作中情人節，黃心穎表示：「重好啦，唔使諗要做乜。」心穎BB咁受歡迎，相信只會煩惱情人節要同邊位追求者一 齊慶祝，而非煩惱要做乜啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/212333_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F212333_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b3099587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於有男粉絲送花又送戒指，黃心穎笑言有點驚嚇。（陳順禎攝）<br />\n<br />\n另外，剛踏入29歲的黃心穎，早已同家人及馬明BB食飯，禮物都收埋，不過，原來好戲在後頭。「昨日出席活動時，有個男fans送花俾我，而紮花中間有隻戒指。」又花又戒指，黃心穎指該男粉絲在場外一直苦等，她一開始也超擔心對方會下跪求婚。「自己見到都嚇一跳，但佢送完花之後又無任何表示，加上我見隻戒指唔係鑽石先敢收。」她又指該名男粉絲連要求合照也沒有，她有感場面尷尬，所以收花後以補妝為理，火速返回後台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/212324_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F212324_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e7c5e8cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽到有粉絲咁厚禮，洪永城問黃心穎私下比咗幾多錢。(陳順禎攝）"},{"pid":"03c291e9c625a7d684c6fc68253c46dcc139c0ad","tid":544431,"uid":91432,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"chicken on the run"},{"pid":"23df2a273e7334064d43f10ac8479bd98628ea31","tid":544431,"uid":9812,"like":108,"dislike":3,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"佢一笑真係好撚柒"},{"pid":"e0e43c2ebdf49504470538a0217d7cf4d1029e66","tid":544431,"uid":163081,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"做返賓妹類角色啱晒佢啦，最佳女演員都有得佢拎"},{"pid":"415d5f8db3f27714ad70bfc3eb037a3a251cd28c","tid":544431,"uid":70391,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:28:50.000Z","msg":"好似力捧佢 俾埋開心速遞主題曲佢唱"},{"pid":"77def83f39fecc0ac5d6c3e2a113d9c786595ba0","tid":544431,"uid":143915,"like":105,"dislike":0,"score":105,"quote":{"pid":"e0e43c2ebdf49504470538a0217d7cf4d1029e66","tid":544431,"uid":163081,"like":183,"dislike":0,"score":183,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"做返賓妹類角色啱晒佢啦，最佳女演員都有得佢拎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:30:19.000Z","msg":"菲籍丫鬟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81a828078be2c5e18d941236f0674e371570529","tid":544431,"uid":86596,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"415d5f8db3f27714ad70bfc3eb037a3a251cd28c","tid":544431,"uid":70391,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:28:50.000Z","msg":"好似力捧佢 俾埋開心速遞主題曲佢唱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:30:37.000Z","msg":"好撚難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696eb30ad191a0f98186f09590c7ffaa0e526ba1","tid":544431,"uid":56240,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"做女主角都係丫鬟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389ccc5439e0fc1c3b37cd6d2cce2ee3ab81d691","tid":544431,"uid":116044,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:31:52.000Z","msg":"個 look 